column2: name
column3: summarize_data

column2: Households by Income
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "household_count",
 by = c("HHFAMINC")
)

column2: Percent Households by Vehicle Frequency, Household MSA Size
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "household_count",
 by = c("MSASIZE","HHVEHCNT"),
 prop = TRUE,
 prop_by = "MSASIZE"
)

column2: Persons by Age
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "person_count",
 by = c("R_AGE")
)

column2: Mean Person Age by Household Size
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "avg",
 agg_var = "R_AGE",
 by = c("HHSIZE")
)

column2: Median Person Age by Educational Attainment
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "median",
 agg_var = "R_AGE",
 by = c("EDUC")
)

column2: Vehicles by Vehicle Type by Census Division
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "vehicle_count",
 by = c("VEHTYPE","CENSUS_D")
)

column2: Mean Vehicle Age By Vehicle Type
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "avg",
 agg_var = "VEHAGE",
 by = c("VEHTYPE"),
 subset = "VEHAGE >=0 & VEHTYPE %in% c('01','02','03','04','05','06')"
)

column2: Median Vehicle Age
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "median",
 agg_var = "VEHAGE",
 subset = "VEHTYPE %in% c('01','02','03','04','05','06')"
)

column2: Person Weekly Walk Trips by Household Life Cycle
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "sum",
 agg_var = "NWALKTRP",
 by = "LIF_CYC"
)

column2: Annual Person Trips by Travel Mode
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "trip_count",
 by = "TRPTRANS"
)

column2: Daily Person Trips
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "person_trip_rate"
)

column2: Daily Household Trips
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "household_trip_rate"
)

column2: Daily Household Trips by Household Size
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "household_trip_rate",

)

column2: Daily Person Trips by Trip Purpose
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,

column2: Daily Person Trips by Sex in South Atlantic Census Division
column3:

 agg = "person_trip_rate",

)

column2: Vehicle Miles of Travel
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "sum",
 agg_var = "TRPMILES",
 subset = "TRPTRANS %in% c('03','04','05','06','08','09','18') & gsub('0','',DRIVER) == '1'"
)

column2: Vehicle Miles of Travel by Person Sex, Census Region
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "sum",
 agg_var = "TRPMILES",
 by = c("R_SEX","CENSUS_R"),
 subset = "TRPTRANS %in% c('03','04','05','06','08','09','18') & gsub('0','',DRIVER) == '1'"
)

column2: Percent of Vehicles by Household MSA Size
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "vehicle_count",
 by = c("MSASIZE"),
 prop = TRUE
)

column2: Percent of Persons by Job Category in 2+ Person Households
column3:
summarize_data(
 data = nhts_data,
 agg = "person_count",
 by = c("OCCAT"),
 prop = TRUE,
 subset = "HHSIZE > 1"
)

column2: Percent of Trips by Trip Purpose, Worker Status
column3:
summarize_data(

 agg = "trip_count",

)
